metadata.description:
The world awakens. Early birds twittering. Some rustling in the leaves. A cloudless sky, a cold night. Tiny condensed water droplets float in the chilly air. Fog hangs over the damp ground of the unfamiliar forest. It obscures the view. What awaits you?

Morning haze has a certain attraction, especially in unfamiliar territory. With a rich imagination, all sorts of things can happen behind the fog. It is a magical phenomenon. The fog can linger, but the first warm rays of sunlight can also dissolve the mist in an instant.

In this work, the morning mist is symbolic. It represents a new beginning. What lies ahead is still uncertain. Everything is possible, but whatever the day may bring, in the end, just like fog, all things pass. 

#Features
- 9 different colors and one in gray scale;
- 4 different layouts (positioning of the vegetation);
- 3 different aspect ratios (1:1, portrait and landscape);
- in 'live mode', click inside the image to save for print;

This artwork requires processing power and is intended for laptops and desktops primarily. It may take some time to render. Please give it some. It's always nice to start a foggy morning calmly. On mobile browsers, animations are disabled.

Generative art coded with p5js.

2022, gpitombo and lucassreveil

